author: Lily Karlin
title: Norman Reedus Makes Epic Entrance At 'Walking Dead' Season 6 Premiere
text:
Tweet Norman Reedus Makes Epic Entrance at 'Walking Dead' Season 6 Premiere! 
Norman Reedus rides into Madison Square Garden on his motorcycle to make the most epic entrance at The Walking Dead season six premiere on Friday (October 9) in New York City. 
The 46-year-old actor was seen posing with co-star Andrew Lincoln inside the event, attended by nearly all the cast members. 
Alanna Masterson also stepped out at the event showing off her baby bump! Like Just Jared on Facebook Credit: Dave Alloca, Larry Busacca, Jamie McCarthy; Photos: Starpix/JustJared, Getty
